author: cmpilato
msg: Finish issue #3752 ("Warn about committing copied directory at depth
'empty'") by only displaying the warning about committing copies at
less-than-infinite depth only when such a copy is being committed.
wrapping notification function and baton for warning about
(svn_cl__commit): Use the copy_warning_notify_func() and baton to
warn about copies instead of a blanket warning for all
non-infinite-depth commits regardless of their targets.
